% Harvested example for FoldList
% src: lib/sli/mathematica.sli:2165
% summary: repeatedly apply a function with two parameters
% synopsis: x [a b c ...] f FoldList -> [f(x,a) f(f(x,a),b) ...]
%
% Examples (verbatim from docstring):
%   0 [1 2 3 4] {add} FoldList gives the cumulative sums of the list.
%            0 [1 2 3 4] {add} FoldList -> [0 1 3 6 10]
